{
  "stem": "4693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next day, I was called in and I was told that he found out that the previous day in Moscow was signed a pact between Poland-- Hitler-- that's what I mean, he didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Russia, that all the individual migration cases are stopped and only will be organized migrations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my wife could not get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She later came out illegally with falsified documents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it was hard for her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She got documents that she was a wife of a Polish officer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, she got documents she was a wife of a Polish general, which I never was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But we falsified documents for her this time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was in Poland two weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was, by this time, already released from the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we escaped Poland in a army truck, Russian army truck, which was delivering mail to the Russian units, between Poland, Czechoslovakia, and Vienna, the Russian part of Vienna.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we got into the truck between the mail and the front of the truck, with the officer sitting in front next of the driver, and a soldier with a rifle sitting in the back.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we got through all the borders and finish in the American zone of Vienna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this how I got out of Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From there--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I found out already in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I found out that my father died from a heart attack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had pneumonia and then he got a heart attack and he died in 1942.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother was taken to Treblinka in 1943.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I found out, as well, during this period, how the Poles behaved.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
